        "description": {
          "value": "<p>As a bonus action, the spirit lamp can open or close its lantern. When open, the lantern sheds bright light in a 30-foot radius and dim light for an additional 30 feet. The spirit lamp can only see objects within the lantern’s light and is blind while the lantern is closed. The lantern’s light pierces magical and nonmagical darkness and can’t be dispelled by magical darkness. If a creature dies in the lantern’s light, its spirit is trapped in the lantern.",
